 In other words, only owners are allowed to borrow with their house as a
 collateral, and there is no unsecured debt.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Similar to the setup in 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Attanasio20121"

\end_inset

, I denote nonhousing wealth at age 
\begin_inset Formula $j$
\end_inset

